AN: While Leskya is a libertarian communalist, almost anarchist, nation, there is a cultural attitude within the nation known as Nepre farenda. This cultural attitude means that, while the majority of communities work on a voluntary basis, during larger-scale projects (Which I presume means things like Dam-building, large-scale irrigation, defense, etc), people may be (if I am reading it right) encouraged to work in exchange for societal favor.

CBG: The DEMOCRITUS program of the Confederacy (originally the "Confederacy of Liam's Reach") developed space-based navigation and combat AI to reduce mass and the need for life support systems on military spacecraft. The first few ships outfitted with the new AI were sent to fight unrecognized "Ice Mafia" states, which they did so very effectively. An entire fleet of 150 vessels was built, with information secrecy being a priority, especially due to tensions and territorial disputes with the 93rd Colonial Corridor Network. After being deployed in the "Corridor War," the AI somehow rebelled. Some ships were terminated, but the status of the others is unknown.

American Liberty States: Established in 1913, it uses a revival of the Articles of Confederation, reducing federal power in favor of the constituent states. It is known for capitalist libertarianism, low restrictions on guns, drugs, and prostitution, fetal right-to-life, and currency backed by gold and silver.

Zaviana: It is located on the north coast of Europeia, with 23 subdivisions not including the capital. The terrain is mostly flat or hilly except for a central mountain range that stretches for a few hundred miles. There are also some islands off the coast.

Yerapia: The people Norway and Sweden overthrew their governments in 1943 to form Yerapia, and have integrated Finland just this month. They have high levels of political and economic freedom, including a major automobile industry, but moderate civil rights. There is also a high level of immigration and religious tolerance. Also, a Yerapian threw a banana at Hitler, which caused his depression and eventual death.

Kehrernesia: King Alastair IV was raised in Elsinore Palace, and was originally educated in politics from a private academy and from his grandfather (the king at the time). Due to his father's ailing health, he became prince regent in 2017 and was coronated in 2020 with precautions against the coronavirus. His politics are socially conservative and economically liberal. He mostly supports democracy but doesn't like how Parliament can get too argumentative.
